UNION ALL

SELECT ''FIELD'' as Type, CAST(f.Id as varchar) as Id, f.Field as Name, ''LineId: '' + CAST(f.LineId as varchar) + '', Key: '' + f.Key as Details
FROM [OCR-Fields] f
INNER JOIN [OCR-Lines] l ON f.LineId = l.Id
INNER JOIN [OCR-Parts] p ON l.PartId = p.Id
WHERE p.TemplateId = 170

ORDER BY Type, Id
")
